<p>
Let $h_n(x) = x \cdot x^{\frac{1}{2n-1}}$ on the interval $[-1,1]$. Then for a fixed $x$ in $[-1,1]$, $\lim h_n(x) = |x|$.
</p>

<p>
    Note that this example is a sequence of differentiable functions that converge to a function which is not differentiable at $0$.
</p>

